# Layer 4 operator extra-terms list (csam_terms_extra.txt) — NOT shipped.
#
# One term per line; '#' comments and blank lines ignored. Case-insensitive
# substring match. Additive only — L4 never overrides L1/L2 decisions.
#
# For operator-specific additions on top of the standard layers. Prefer
# authoritative indicator lists (INHOPE/IWF/NCMEC) over ad-hoc terms to keep
# false positives low (e.g. short ambiguous tokens inside innocent words).
#
# Absent/empty -> Layer 4 inactive. Hot-reloadable (~30s).
#
# (Intentionally empty — populate locally; template only.)
